sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as app-admin / app-api-ts
    participant Connectors as app-connectors
    participant Worker as app-api worker
    participant Vendor as API fournisseur
    participant Store as payload store
    participant DB as Postgres / integration_*

    Admin->>Connectors: create connection + test + triggerSync()
    Connectors-->>Admin: run queued
    Worker->>Connectors: POST /v1/runtime/sync-runs/claim
    Connectors-->>Worker: claimed run
    Worker->>Connectors: POST /execution-plan
    Connectors-->>Worker: connection + credentials + syncState
    Worker->>Connectors: GET /access-context
    Connectors-->>Worker: provider runtime context
    Worker->>Vendor: fetch source objects
    Vendor-->>Worker: records
    Worker->>Connectors: POST /provider-events
    Connectors->>Store: persist payloads bruts
    Connectors-->>Worker: raw event summaries
    Worker->>DB: ingest raw events / update sync state / complete run
